title: Britney Spears - Ooh La La (from The Smurfs 2)[1080p x264]-{BFAB
description:
"Ooh La La" is a song by American recording artist Britney Spears. It was released on June 17, 2013, by Kemosabe Records and RCA Records as the lead single from the soundtrack of the 2013 family film The Smurfs 2. It was written by Lukasz "Dr. Luke" Gottwald, Joshua "Ammo" Coleman, Lola Blanc, Francisca Hall, Henry "Cirkut" Walter, Bonnie McKee, and Jacob Kasher Hindlin.The music video was filmed in June and was directed by Marc Klasfeld. The video features appearances by Spears's children, Sean Preston and Jayden James Federline, as well as a brief appearance by Spears' niece, Maddie Aldridge. The video premiered on Spears' Vevo channel at 12PM ET on July 11 ,2013.MSN Music noted the opening scene from the "Ooh La La" video pays homage to Janet Jackson's "Nasty" video, saying "The clip plays out like a more kid-friendly version of Janet Jackson's "Nasty" video, with Spears and her kids taking in a movie when mom is suddenly transported into the on-screen action."
